<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Welcome!</b></font>

28
00:01:44,714 --> 00:01:46,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey, Takumi!</b></font>

29
00:01:46,114 --> 00:01:47,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Is Itsuki here?</b></font>

30
00:01:47,884 --> 00:01:50,454
