48
00:02:56,554 --> 00:02:59,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The best thing is to just
leave him be for a while.</b></font>

49
00:02:59,924 --> 00:03:03,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Listen, when Itsuki comes
