52
00:03:07,294 --> 00:03:10,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Yessir.
--Understood.</b></font>

53
00:03:18,774 --> 00:03:21,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>High octane. Fill 'er up.</b></font>

54
00:03:21,144 --> 00:03:23,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yes, sir. Thanks very much!</b></font>

55
00:03:28,414 --> 00:03:30,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hello. Thank you for the other day.</b></font>

56
00:03:30,484 --> 00:03:33,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey. This is perfect timing.</b></font>

57
00:03:33,154 --> 00:03:35,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There's something I want to talk to you about.</b></font>

58
00:03:35,224 --> 00:03:37,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There is?</b></font>

59
00:03:37,824 --> 00:03:42,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Act 15: 4WD Complex"</b></font>

60
00:03:50,474 --> 00:03:54,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I can't control how things turned out,
