62
00:03:57,244 --> 00:04:02,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He should hurry up and forget Kazumi's
ugly ass and find himself a good woman.</b></font>

63
00:04:16,464 --> 00:04:19,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This is how the power
of a supercharger feels...</b></font>

64
00:04:19,604 --> 00:04:22,134
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's completely different from my Eight-Six.</b></font>

65
00:04:22,134 --> 00:04:26,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This thing easily clocks
over 200 on a chassis dynamo,</b></font>

66
00:04:26,204 --> 00:04:31,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but on a high-speed stage like Akina,
it's not so good on extended uphills.</b></font>

67
00:04:31,484 --> 00:04:35,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It sure feels good on Chichibu's
narrow mountain roads, though.</b></font>

68
00:04:46,064 --> 00:04:48,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>So now that you've beaten
the Northwest Area coalition,</b></font>

69
00:04:48,564 --> 00:04:51,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>you're undefeated in Saitama, huh?</b></font>

70
00:04:54,674 --> 00:04:59,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Still, there is just one
bothersome group left standing...</b></font>

71
00:05:01,474 --> 00:05:03,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They're a little full of themselves.</b></font>

72
00:05:03,814 --> 00:05:07,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>In terms of skill, they probably
won't give you too hard a time.</b></font>

73
00:05:10,684 --> 00:05:12,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Um...</b></font>

74
00:05:12,884 --> 00:05:16,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I've wanted to ask you this...</b></font>

75
00:05:16,994 --> 00:05:18,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Do you feel there's some kind of limit</b></font>

76
00:05:18,864 --> 00:05:22,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>with the Eight-Six's power
or racing capabilities?</b></font>

77
00:05:22,894 --> 00:05:25,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Well, yeah. Of course there is.</b></font>

78
00:05:25,764 --> 00:05:29,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's why I added the turbo,
then the supercharger,</b></font>

79
00:05:29,034 --> 00:05:32,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and am always fiddling with it.</b></font>

80
00:05:32,404 --> 00:05:35,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That last race I did in the rain,
just how old the car's basic design is</b></font>

81
00:05:35,914 --> 00:05:40,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>hit me really hard, like a body blow.</b></font>

82
00:05:40,714 --> 00:05:43,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Even you think the same thing, huh?</b></font>

83
00:05:43,384 --> 00:05:48,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If so, that's unexpected. I think
you're in a class all your own.</b></font>

84
00:05:48,594 --> 00:05:52,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Even in this day and age, you're winning
race after race, undefeated, in an Eight-Six!</b></font>

85
00:05:52,794 --> 00:05:57,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No... Actually, I haven't
told anyone this yet, but...</b></font>

86
00:05:57,104 --> 00:06:00,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Recently, somebody beat me.</b></font>

87
00:06:09,414 --> 00:06:11,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I can't believe it.</b></font>

88
00:06:11,644 --> 00:06:15,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Your Eight-Six, beaten on
your own home turf...</b></font>

89
00:06:15,584 --> 00:06:18,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--What kind of car?
--An Impreza.</b></font>

90
00:06:18,624 --> 00:06:20,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>A four-wheel drive, huh?</b></font>

91
00:06:20,654 --> 00:06:23,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's been driving me crazy ever since.</b></font>

92
00:06:23,994 --> 00:06:28,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's like I've developed
some kind of 4WD complex.</b></font>

93
00:06:28,094 --> 00:06:29,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You say that,</b></font>

94
00:06:29,594 --> 00:06:33,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but you've beaten Lancer Evos before, right?</b></font>

95
00:06:33,004 --> 00:06:36,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't you think it's best not to give 4WD
any kind of special consideration?</b></font>

96
00:06:36,834 --> 00:06:40,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm trying to convince myself that, but...</b></font>

97
00:06:44,744 --> 00:06:49,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>In any case, the impact of it was far too strong.</b></font>

98
00:06:49,184 --> 00:06:52,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's why I was wondering
what you thought about it.</b></font>

99
00:06:52,624 --> 00:06:54,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Well...</b></font>

100
00:06:56,924 --> 00:07:01,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm running up against the
Eight-Six's limits too, and I don't like it.</b></font>

101
00:07:01,494 --> 00:07:04,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>To be honest, it's not just 4WDs.</b></font>

102
00:07:04,804 --> 00:07:08,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's FFs and FRs...
I'm scared of all the new cars.</b></font>

103
00:07:08,834 --> 00:07:10,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>All of them?</b></font>

104
00:07:10,174 --> 00:07:14,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But I've used that complex as a
way to spring back even harder.</b></font>

105
00:07:14,644 --> 00:07:16,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm refining my techniques,</b></font>

106
00:07:16,474 --> 00:07:19,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and using my skills to cover
the difference in car functionality.</b></font>

107
00:07:20,814 --> 00:07:23,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Look, let me tell you something.</b></font>

108
00:07:23,984 --> 00:07:27,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This is actually the perfect chance to
get rid of this weird hang-up of yours.</b></font>

109
00:07:27,994 --> 00:07:31,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I think your next opponent will be a 4WD.</b></font>

110
00:07:31,894 --> 00:07:33,964
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Up till last year,</b></font>

111
00:07:33,964 --> 00:07:38,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>you could keep on winning, having nothing
to do with theory or even being in the know,</b></font>

112
00:07:38,704 --> 00:07:43,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but once you've reached a certain level,
you're bound to run into its limitations.</b></font>

113
00:07:43,904 --> 00:07:46,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>For example, you don't
really know what 4WD is,</b></font>

114
00:07:46,974 --> 00:07:49,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but you race your hardest
against it and end up winning.</b></font>

115
00:07:49,974 --> 00:07:57,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>In a way, it's a fool's victory. But I think
that's also your greatest strength.</b></font>

116
00:07:57,014 --> 00:08:02,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What's being demanded of you now is that
you understand the characteristics of 4WD,</b></font>

117
00:08:02,224 --> 00:08:07,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and that you negate your enemy's
strengths and attack his weaknesses.</b></font>

118
00:08:07,094 --> 00:08:09,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>In other words, you win smart.</b></font>

119
00:08:09,864 --> 00:08:12,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I think this next race will
be a good chance for you.</b></font>

120
00:08:12,504 --> 00:08:14,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Why not think in your own way,</b></font>

121
00:08:14,434 --> 00:08:17,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and try drawing up an attack
plan for tackling a 4WD?</b></font>

122
00:08:19,074 --> 00:08:22,444
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>An attack plan for a 4WD...</i></b></font>

123
00:08:22,444 --> 00:08:26,444
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Still, it'd be boring if you
started getting too clever.</b></font>

124
00:08:26,444 --> 00:08:31,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's letting that "fool's power" of yours
run wild that makes you <i>you.</i></b></font>

125
00:08:32,354 --> 00:08:36,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Fujiwara Tofu Shop"</b></font>

126
00:08:37,464 --> 00:08:41,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>A 4WD's strengths and weaknesses, huh?</i></b></font>

127
00:08:44,064 --> 00:08:46,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Sure enough, like Wataru said,</i></b></font>

128
00:08:46,734 --> 00:08:51,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>last year I just raced my hardest,</i>
<i>not knowing anything.</i></b></font>

129
00:08:54,114 --> 00:08:59,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Now I know all too well what 4WD is about...</i></b></font>

130
00:08:59,084 --> 00:09:02,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>But it's not as simple as that.</i></b></font>

131
00:09:04,284 --> 00:09:05,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>This thing...</i></b></font>

132
00:09:05,724 --> 00:09:08,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Does it even have anything that</i>
<i>could be called a weakness?</i></b></font>

133
00:09:22,904 --> 00:09:24,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Well, what did you wanna talk about?</b></font>

134
00:09:24,904 --> 00:09:27,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This is just between us, but...</b></font>

135
00:09:27,314 --> 00:09:31,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If we win this next race,
it'll mean some money.</b></font>

136
00:09:31,514 --> 00:09:35,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They're famous, right? Project D.</b></font>

137
00:09:35,314 --> 00:09:38,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Think about it: What if our Lancer Evos win?</b></font>

138
00:09:38,184 --> 00:09:40,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Being the shop that worked on those cars</b></font>

139
00:09:40,624 --> 00:09:44,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>has more advertising potential
than you can imagine.</b></font>

140
00:09:44,324 --> 00:09:46,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If you really promoted it on the Internet,</b></font>

141
00:09:46,594 --> 00:09:48,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I bet there'd be a huge increase in customers.</b></font>

142
00:09:48,994 --> 00:09:53,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Okay, I follow. So how much
are we talking about?</b></font>

143
00:09:53,104 --> 00:09:57,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If we win both races, 500,000 yen.
One race, 250,000.</b></font>

144
00:09:57,674 --> 00:10:01,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If it's a draw, let's say 50,000 yen.</b></font>

145
00:10:01,374 --> 00:10:02,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Are you serious?</b></font>

146
00:10:02,974 --> 00:10:04,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>M'yeah.</b></font>

147
00:10:04,044 --> 00:10:08,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But winning ain't gonna be easy.</b></font>

148
00:10:08,114 --> 00:10:11,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'd never planned on running a "clean" race.</b></font>

149
00:10:11,184 --> 00:10:17,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If a little underhandedness
can get results, so be it.</b></font>

150
00:10:17,154 --> 00:10:21,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>And that's your specialty, right?
Underhandedness.</b></font>

151
00:10:21,294 --> 00:10:24,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Not that I wanna hear that from you, but yeah.</b></font>

152
00:10:28,874 --> 00:10:33,304
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Corporate Reforestation"</b></font>

153
00:10:33,644 --> 00:10:35,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--They're here!
--Here we go!</b></font>

154
00:11:05,244 --> 00:11:11,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Just like Wataru said... 4WDs.</i>
<i>They've got Lancer Evos, huh?</i></b></font>

155
00:11:12,914 --> 00:11:15,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Ryosuke, come here a minute.</b></font>

156
00:11:19,424 --> 00:11:24,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>These guys say they want to split the
practice time and get some racing in, too.</b></font>

157
00:11:24,064 --> 00:11:27,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We've never done it that way
before, so... What should we do?</b></font>

158
00:11:27,894 --> 00:11:32,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't understand why we have to split
the time. Can't we practice together?</b></font>

159
00:11:32,534 --> 00:11:36,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The thing is, we don't
like that idea. Sorry, but...</b></font>

160
00:11:36,704 --> 00:11:42,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We don't wanna race with guys when
we don't even know how good they are.</b></font>

161
00:11:43,374 --> 00:11:46,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Goin' out too far on a corner and... Hmph!</b></font>

162
00:11:46,644 --> 00:11:50,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Smashin' headlong into an oncomin'
car ain't my idea of a good time.</b></font>

163
00:11:50,454 --> 00:11:53,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're saying you don't
trust our driving abilities?</b></font>

164
00:11:53,284 --> 00:11:56,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--You stay out of this, Keisuke.
--But...</b></font>

165
00:11:56,294 --> 00:11:59,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey! All I'm askin' is you be fair</b></font>

166
00:11:59,764 --> 00:12:03,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and give us half the time till mornin', right?</b></font>

167
00:12:03,394 --> 00:12:05,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What's with the friggin' attitude?!</b></font>

168
00:12:05,634 --> 00:12:09,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If you got a problem,
then just forget the whole thing.</b></font>

169
00:12:09,474 --> 00:12:14,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It ain't like there's some big reason
we gotta go out of our way to race ya.</b></font>

170
00:12:16,914 --> 00:12:18,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Let's do it.</b></font>

171
00:12:18,144 --> 00:12:19,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Ryosuke...</b></font>

172
00:12:19,684 --> 00:12:20,954
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Big brother!</b></font>

173
00:12:20,954 --> 00:12:22,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Let's get going.</b></font>

174
00:12:38,334 --> 00:12:39,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What a joke.</b></font>

175
00:12:39,804 --> 00:12:42,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What the hell's he talking about, "fair"?</b></font>

176
00:12:42,174 --> 00:12:45,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This is their home course,
the one they always run.</b></font>

177
00:12:45,874 --> 00:12:49,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The truth is, they just don't
want us to practice, right?</b></font>

178
00:12:49,014 --> 00:12:52,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We've never met anyone like them before,
have we? They really piss me off.</b></font>

179
00:12:52,684 --> 00:12:56,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Up till now, sure they've come up
with their own strategies,</b></font>

180
00:12:56,114 --> 00:12:59,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but everyone we've raced
has fought a fair, clean fight.</b></font>

181
00:12:59,524 --> 00:13:02,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Well, if they think cutting
our practice time in half</b></font>

182
00:13:02,994 --> 00:13:05,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>will give them an advantage,
they couldn't be more wrong.</b></font>

183
00:13:05,794 --> 00:13:10,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Come tomorrow, we'll be giving them a
lesson in the true power of Project D!</b></font>

184
00:13:10,164 --> 00:13:12,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Depending on how you look at it,</b></font>

185
00:13:12,804 --> 00:13:16,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>this could be a good experience
for Fujiwara as well, right?</b></font>

186
00:13:16,034 --> 00:13:19,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He'll have to come up with
a strategy for the course</b></font>

187
00:13:19,244 --> 00:13:22,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and get his car ready in half the time.</b></font>

188
00:13:22,174 --> 00:13:24,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Which would be fine, if that's all this is.</b></font>

189
00:13:24,984 --> 00:13:27,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I have a very bad feeling about this.</b></font>

190
00:13:27,014 --> 00:13:28,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>A bad feeling?</b></font>

191
00:13:28,814 --> 00:13:33,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There's something we haven't seen yet.
Don't let your guard down, Fumihiro.</b></font>

192
00:13:52,244 --> 00:13:56,444
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Burn both the road surface and
course topography into memory.</b></font>

193
00:13:59,114 --> 00:14:03,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>For crying out loud. Finally!
We get to go now, huh?</b></font>

194
00:14:04,784 --> 00:14:09,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You guys keep standing around and
it'll be morning. Let's get a move on!</b></font>

195
00:14:11,894 --> 00:14:14,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Ready and standing by. Shall we go, Keisuke?</b></font>

196
00:14:14,894 --> 00:14:16,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah.</b></font>

197
00:14:33,484 --> 00:14:37,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We don't have much time,
so we'll have to make this count.</b></font>

198
00:14:37,054 --> 00:14:39,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Understood. Here we go.</b></font>

199
00:14:49,294 --> 00:14:52,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They better enjoy themselves while they can.</b></font>

200
00:14:52,834 --> 00:14:57,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I think your best bet is to go for
the FD rather than the Eight-Six.</b></font>

201
00:14:57,674 --> 00:15:00,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're not tryin' to make things
easier just for yourself, are you?</b></font>

202
00:15:00,644 --> 00:15:06,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No, I ain't. That guy in the FD
really pissed me off.</b></font>

203
00:15:06,744 --> 00:15:10,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He looked at me and scowled, the bastard.</b></font>

204
00:15:10,154 --> 00:15:14,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I wanna make that uppity little brat cry!</b></font>

205
00:15:14,354 --> 00:15:20,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Fine, okay. We split the money
we get right down the middle.</b></font>

206
00:15:22,664 --> 00:15:26,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hello? It's me. You ready?</b></font>

207
00:15:26,804 --> 00:15:28,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The target is...</b></font>

208
00:15:28,834 --> 00:15:30,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...the FD.</b></font>

209
00:15:32,844 --> 00:15:37,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Are we really gonna do this? If we
get busted, there's gonna be trouble.</b></font>

210
00:15:37,314 --> 00:15:39,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Just do it.</b></font>

211
00:15:39,014 --> 00:15:43,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Understood. I don't know how
good our aim will be, though.</b></font>

212
00:15:43,614 --> 00:15:46,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If we're off, we could get both cars.</b></font>

213
00:15:46,024 --> 00:15:48,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If it happens, it happens.</b></font>

214
00:15:51,464 --> 00:15:53,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He says the target is the FD.</b></font>

215
00:16:20,724 --> 00:16:25,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Having our practice time</i>
<i>cut in half really stings.</i></b></font>

216
00:16:25,194 --> 00:16:28,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I don't have the luxury of thinking</i>
<i>about how to battle a 4WD...</i></b></font>

217
00:16:28,064 --> 00:16:30,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Right now, I just have to</i>
<i>concentrate on the course!</i></b></font>

218
00:16:32,004 --> 00:16:34,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>These cracks in the road make the car bounce.</i></b></font>

219
00:16:34,204 --> 00:16:37,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I have to remember all the cracked areas!</i></b></font>

220
00:16:40,204 --> 00:16:44,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The road sur face is a bit rough, but there's</i>
<i>really nothing to this course at all.</i></b></font>

221
00:17:02,094 --> 00:17:04,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Practice is a lot of fun.</i></b></font>

222
00:17:04,234 --> 00:17:09,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Every time I pass him like that, I think</i>
<i>to myself, "I ain't losin' to him!"</i></b></font>

223
00:17:18,444 --> 00:17:23,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The FD feels good today. At this rate,</i>
<i>it should be ready to race in no time.</i></b></font>

224
00:17:23,584 --> 00:17:26,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I'll friggin' show you how it's done!</i></b></font>

225
00:17:36,094 --> 00:17:39,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>There's something flowing... Water?</i></b></font>

226
00:17:39,264 --> 00:17:41,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>There was nothing there earlier.</i></b></font>

227
00:17:41,774 --> 00:17:44,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>It's not water! Oh, no!</i></b></font>

228
00:18:10,464 --> 00:18:12,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hello, Fumihiro? It's Keisuke.</b></font>

229
00:18:12,864 --> 00:18:14,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah. What's up?</b></font>

230
00:18:14,434 --> 00:18:16,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Are those guys still there?</b></font>

231
00:18:16,334 --> 00:18:19,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>By "those guys," you mean
the ones we're racing?</b></font>

232
00:18:19,774 --> 00:18:23,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They left a little while ago. Is everything okay?</b></font>

233
00:18:23,014 --> 00:18:24,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hell no, it's not okay!</b></font>

234
00:18:24,984 --> 00:18:28,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This is an emergency. Stop the Eight-Six.
Do <i>not</i> let him come back this way!</b></font>

235
00:18:28,784 --> 00:18:31,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What's going on?</b></font>

236
00:18:31,284 --> 00:18:34,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Somebody tossed a bunch of oil
all over the goddamn road!</b></font>

237
00:18:34,854 --> 00:18:36,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What?!</b></font>

238
00:18:36,324 --> 00:18:39,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>So, are you all right?</b></font>

239
00:18:39,524 --> 00:18:43,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I... I'm fine, but...</b></font>

240
00:18:43,634 --> 00:18:46,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...the FD is screwed up.</b></font>

241
00:18:55,044 --> 00:18:59,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This is terrible. There's no way anyone
could've avoided this. Not even Keisuke.</b></font>

242
00:18:59,844 --> 00:19:01,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Who would do this?</b></font>

243
00:19:01,654 --> 00:19:04,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's obvious! Who the hell else was here?!</b></font>

244
00:19:04,584 --> 00:19:09,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Whoever spilled this oil
probably fled via that side road.</b></font>

245
00:19:09,994 --> 00:19:13,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>According to the map, the road
is just wide enough to fit one car</b></font>

246
00:19:13,764 --> 00:19:15,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and runs to the next city.</b></font>

247
00:19:15,434 --> 00:19:18,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Then if we hurry and get over
there to the other end first,</b></font>

248
00:19:18,934 --> 00:19:23,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>we can seize the idiot by the neck
as he comes sauntering out!</b></font>

249
00:19:23,174 --> 00:19:25,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm taking Van #1, brother.</b></font>

250
00:19:25,544 --> 00:19:27,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll go with you, Keisuke!</b></font>

251
00:19:27,174 --> 00:19:29,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Stop, Keisuke. It's a waste of time.</b></font>

252
00:19:29,844 --> 00:19:33,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But brother! I can't just let this go!</b></font>

253
00:19:33,714 --> 00:19:36,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>How can I stand by when they've
wrecked my precious FD?!</b></font>

254
00:19:36,854 --> 00:19:39,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We've gotta grab 'em and
knock the hell out of 'em!</b></font>

255
00:19:39,354 --> 00:19:43,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm telling you to control yourself.
Don't go running off half-cocked!</b></font>

256
00:19:46,894 --> 00:19:50,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--How is it?
--It's going to be a bit of work.</b></font>

257
00:19:50,394 --> 00:19:54,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The suspension arm is damaged,
and after an impact like that,</b></font>

258
00:19:54,574 --> 00:19:56,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>we're going to have to
check the alignment, too.</b></font>

259
00:19:56,974 --> 00:20:01,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There is 100% no way it can
be ready by tomorrow night.</b></font>

260
00:20:01,104 --> 00:20:03,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There's nothing wrong
with the drive system, right?!</b></font>

261
00:20:03,574 --> 00:20:05,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Do something to make it run!</b></font>

262
00:20:05,584 --> 00:20:08,954
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Make some emergency repairs!
It doesn't even have to run in a straight line!</b></font>

263
00:20:08,954 --> 00:20:11,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll make it work somehow!</b></font>

264
00:20:11,224 --> 00:20:16,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't talk foolishness, Keisuke. If a
car's got trouble with its underbody,</b></font>

265
00:20:16,224 --> 00:20:18,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>pushing it to the limit amounts to suicide.</b></font>

266
00:20:18,424 --> 00:20:22,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He's right. There's no telling
how the car will behave.</b></font>

267
00:20:22,934 --> 00:20:27,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Its limits have been pushed way down...
Racing it in this state would be impossible.</b></font>

268
00:20:35,974 --> 00:20:40,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Oh dear, oh dear. I thought
things were a bit too quiet.</b></font>

269
00:20:40,244 --> 00:20:43,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You got into a wreck <i>here</i>?</b></font>

270
00:20:49,654 --> 00:20:52,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That was a pretty damn rotten trick you pulled.</b></font>

271
00:20:52,824 --> 00:20:55,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You all did this, didn't you?! That oil!</b></font>

272
00:20:55,534 --> 00:21:02,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't follow. What're ya talkin' about?
Enough with the weird accusations already.</b></font>

273
00:21:02,374 --> 00:21:06,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Well? You got any proof it was us that did it?</b></font>

274
00:21:06,544 --> 00:21:10,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't screw with me!
I don't need proof, I frickin' <i>know</i>!</b></font>

275
00:21:10,514 --> 00:21:12,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Now quit flappin' your mouth
and get outta that damn car!</b></font>

276
00:21:12,514 --> 00:21:14,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Stop it, Keisuke.</b></font>

277
00:21:14,814 --> 00:21:17,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Oooh, what a surprise!</b></font>

278
00:21:17,814 --> 00:21:22,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This "Project D" team of yours
has a real attitude problem, huh?</b></font>

279
00:21:22,324 --> 00:21:26,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah, I get it. Not only do ya make
accusations without any proof,</b></font>

280
00:21:26,724 --> 00:21:28,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>you go around threatenin' the
people you're supposed to race!</b></font>

281
00:21:28,834 --> 00:21:34,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Eeew, that's so uncool. I wouldn't
wanna race people like that!</b></font>

282
00:21:36,134 --> 00:21:39,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm sorry. Please forgive us.</b></font>

283
00:21:39,144 --> 00:21:44,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>As you can see, our hillclimb
car has gotten into a wreck.</b></font>

284
00:21:44,044 --> 00:21:47,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's been badly damaged,
and it won't be fixed soon.</b></font>

285
00:21:47,014 --> 00:21:50,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah, well, that's a shame.</b></font>

286
00:21:50,484 --> 00:21:56,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm sorry for the inconvenience, but could
we possibly postpone our race for a week?</b></font>

287
00:21:56,694 --> 00:21:58,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>A week, huh?</b></font>

288
00:21:58,664 --> 00:22:02,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yes. We would definitely be ready
within that amount of time.</b></font>

289
00:22:02,334 --> 00:22:07,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I get it. I know just what you're sayin'.</b></font>

290
00:22:07,334 --> 00:22:10,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But the answer is, "No."</b></font>

291
00:22:10,234 --> 00:22:16,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We ain't made of free time, you know.
I got me a date next weekend.</b></font>

292
00:22:16,014 --> 00:22:18,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Bastard!</i></b></font>

293
00:22:18,244 --> 00:22:24,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>In motorsport, a car that don't make it to
the startin' line is automatically the loser.</b></font>

294
00:22:24,454 --> 00:22:28,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Whatever you all's circumstances,
it's got nothin' to do with us.</b></font>

295
00:22:28,794 --> 00:22:32,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Right? Or am I wrong?</b></font>

296
00:22:32,294 --> 00:22:35,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We start at 8:00 tonight, as agreed.</b></font>

297
00:22:35,734 --> 00:22:38,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Use the Eight-Six or
somethin' instead, whatever.</b></font>

298
00:22:38,364 --> 00:22:44,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't forget, if yer even
one minute late, you all lose.</b></font>

299
00:22:48,814 --> 00:22:50,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Shit!</b></font>

300
00:22:50,074 --> 00:22:52,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That guy's gettin' on my last goddamn nerve!</b></font>

301
00:22:52,284 --> 00:22:55,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We have no time for you to take your
frustrations out on the guardrail.</b></font>

302
00:22:55,554 --> 00:22:59,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Fujiwara and Matsumoto, you work
on setting up the Eight-Six.</b></font>

303
00:22:59,084 --> 00:23:00,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Okay.
--Understood.</b></font>

304
00:23:00,884 --> 00:23:06,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>However, run the course in halves until
we've finished cleaning up the oil.</b></font>

305
00:23:06,924 --> 00:23:11,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>All other personnel are on oil detail.
We don't have time. Hurry!</b></font>

306
00:23:11,664 --> 00:23:13,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hold on!</b></font>

307
00:23:13,564 --> 00:23:15,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What am I supposed to do?</b></font>

308
00:23:15,434 --> 00:23:17,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Brother, aren't we going to try fixing the FD?</b></font>

309
00:23:17,904 --> 00:23:19,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If we did, it would be a wasted effort.</b></font>

310
00:23:19,774 --> 00:23:24,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I have explored all options, and my
conclusion is that it is not possible.</b></font>

311
00:23:24,844 --> 00:23:29,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There isn't enough time.
Your role in this race is no more.</b></font>

312
00:23:29,084 --> 00:23:30,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You shall stay on the sidelines.</b></font>

313
00:23:30,084 --> 00:23:32,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Brother, please let me race!</b></font>

314
00:23:32,084 --> 00:23:34,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>At this rate, we're just
playing right into their hands!</b></font>

315
00:23:34,624 --> 00:23:39,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Do you still not understand, Keisuke?
The blame for the FD's crash lies with you.</b></font>

316
00:23:39,594 --> 00:23:41,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Huh?</b></font>

317
00:23:41,594 --> 00:23:47,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yes. If it were me, I would not have crashed
my car over a simple trick like that.</b></font>

318
00:23:47,804 --> 00:23:53,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This was caused by ego and lack of attention.
Calm yourself and think this over!</b></font>

319
00:23:53,174 --> 00:23:55,444
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Let's get to work.</b></font>

320
00:24:05,224 --> 00:24:11,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I... I can't accept this.
Ryosuke is being too harsh.</b></font>

321
00:24:11,054 --> 00:24:15,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There's no way so much oil
could have been avoided.</b></font>

322
00:24:15,494 --> 00:24:18,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No matter how you look at it,
it's just not possible!</b></font>

323
00:24:20,334 --> 00:24:21,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No.</b></font>

324
00:24:21,804 --> 00:24:28,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>My brother could do it. He could've
cleared that oil spill like it was nothing.</b></font>

325
00:24:28,244 --> 00:24:33,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's just like he said, Kenta.
And the truth is, I know it.</b></font>

326
00:24:33,884 --> 00:24:40,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm angry at myself for falling
right into a cheap trick like that.</b></font>

327
00:24:40,154 --> 00:24:44,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's exactly why,
no matter what, I <i>have</i> to race!</b></font>

328
00:24:44,724 --> 00:24:49,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What should I do? Tell me, Kenta!</b></font>

329
00:24:49,564 --> 00:24:52,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Keisuke!</b></font>

330
00:24:57,404 --> 00:25:01,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Keisuke wants to race, but can't.</i>
<i>If I think about how he feels too much,</i></b></font>

331
00:25:01,344 --> 00:25:05,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I start feeling mixed up myself. But...!</i></b></font>

332
00:25:07,184 --> 00:25:11,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Right now, all I can do is give my total</i>
<i>concentration to the job I've been given.</i></b></font>

333
00:25:11,724 --> 00:25:15,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>And I will definitely win. I'll beat them!</i></b></font>

334
00:25:21,194 --> 00:25:25,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>A rose that's bloomed on the battlefield,</i>
<i>for the reason they don't know</i></b></font>

335
00:25:25,204 --> 00:25:29,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>A caterpillar that can only move forward</i>
<i>tramples it under foot again today</i></b></font>

336
00:25:29,074 --> 00:25:33,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Yo, hates and pain, increasing only hatred</i></b></font>

337
00:25:33,374 --> 00:25:37,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Hates and pain, with those</i>
<i>social conditions transmitted live</i></b></font>

338
00:25:37,474 --> 00:25:46,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Hold me with stronger hands</i></b></font>

339
00:25:46,224 --> 00:25:52,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Your voice in a restless night</i>
<i>(For the reason they don't know)</i></b></font>

340
00:25:52,394 --> 00:25:58,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The world will someday be shedding blood</i>
<i>(All around the world)</i></b></font>

341
00:25:58,464 --> 00:26:08,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Let me forget that kind of news,</i>
<i>I don't want to understand</i></b></font>

342
00:26:09,574 --> 00:26:16,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Nobody reason, nobody sure where is the end</i></b></font>

343
00:26:16,614 --> 00:26:25,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Ah, sing gently just a little more, even if it's a lie</i></b></font>

344
00:26:25,164 --> 00:26:29,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Check it, conflicting information is</i>
<i>already reported by the mass media</i></b></font>

345
00:26:29,164 --> 00:26:33,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The outnumbered convey the</i>
<i>deep fears of the whole situation</i></b></font>

346
00:26:33,204 --> 00:26:37,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Reason is flammable, an age</i>
<i>lacking the power of restraint, yeah</i></b></font>

347
00:26:37,204 --> 00:26:41,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Devoting yourself body and spirit,</i>
<i>you keep receiving that baptism</i></b></font>

348
00:26:41,504 --> 00:26:48,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Nobody reason, nobody sure where is the end</i></b></font>

349
00:26:48,514 --> 00:26:57,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>If rowing a boat that's untrustworthy</i>
<i>and on the verge of breaking...</i></b></font>

350
00:26:57,454 --> 00:27:04,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Nobody reason, no one</i>
<i>confess that it was wrong</i></b></font>

351
00:27:04,534 --> 00:27:14,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Ah, sing gently just a little more, even if it's a lie</i></b></font>

